Rod of Extrapolation   100   1      135     225   0.60  135    225    35   35%   0.16
Rod of Imaginos         75   1      100     125   0.80  100    125    25   33%   0.20</pre><!--EZCODE CODE END--><br>
The problem I see here is that for other users it is more efficient in terms of hit points to mana AND that 25 mana may not be significant.  35 mana may not be significant either, I may have to return to the drawing board on that one.<br>
<br>
But I think that adding another charge to <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> Mod Rod</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> at 44th would allow the role of mana transference and regeneration to occur at a lower level, and one where those considerations begin to assume significance.<br>
